definitions.definition: ( historical ) The former currency of Japan until 1870, before the yen .
The badge or emblem of a Japanese family , especially a family of the ancient feudal nobility ; typically circular and consists of conventionalized forms from nature .

main_definition: ( historical ) The former currency of Japan until 1870, before the yen .

definitions.definition: ( colloquial ) Man ; used in places such as Jamaica , and Lancashire , Shropshire and the Black Country in England .

definitions.definition: A creature in a video game , usually one which is captured, trained up and used in battles.
A video game or anime in which catching and battling creatures is an important element.
